Package ie.ucd.nearmiss

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControllerThread
    Thread which controls the updating of models and instructing the models to draw themselves.
    Game
    Game View which Handles the Interaction Between the Game Controller and the Models for Each Sprite
    GamePlayingDownUnitTest
    Checks that the plane is going down the screen when the user is not touching the screen.
    GamePlayingUpUnitTest
    Checks that the plane goes up the screen when the user is touching the screen.
    GameStartUnitTest
    Check that the game objects are not moving when the user launches the game.
    MainActivity
    Activity that launches when the app is started.
    Obstacle
    Obstacles Class which Creates and Gives a Speed to an Obstacle
    Plane
    Class which models the Plane.
    Sky
    Class which models the Sky.
    SkyMovingUnitTest
    Checks that the sky has moved and is moving at the specified rate (-5px/ms) Instrumentation test, which will execute on an Android device.
    Sprite
    Abstract lass which describes movable objects in the game.
